External Knowledge:
- 'sets of twins' refers to pairs of duplicate questions;
- 'identity of the first twin' refers to the question ID and the user who posted it;
- 'birthdate' refers to the post date of the question;
- 'the number of times it was visited' refers to the views the question has received;
- 'family resemblance score' refers to the similarity score between the duplicate questions.
